<p>
<lb n="1"/>gahapatino savarasa putasa mahānāvikasa sivakasa 
<lb n="2"/><unclear>bha</unclear>riyāya gharaniya Utaradataya s<unclear>i</unclear>dhatham<unclear>i</unclear>taya sapatikāya 
<lb n="3"/><unclear>sa</unclear>duhutukāya samit<unclear>ā</unclear>macāya Ayaka0<unclear>tha</unclear>bha <unclear>de</unclear>yadhama</p>
</div>
<div type="apparatus">
	<listApp>
		<app loc="2">
		<lem>Utaradataya</lem>
		<note>Vogel suggested that this could possibly be restored to <foreign>utara-duhutaya</foreign>.</note>
